... on a second thought, this is probably the intended solution (and it works):

*** sipp-3.5.1/src/socket.cpp	Thu Mar 17 09:05:49 2016
--- sipp-3.5.1/src/socket.cpp.new	Thu Feb 15 12:57:22 2018
